<a href="/questions/539946-has-anyone-else-tied-the-revelations-in">Has anyone else tied the revelations in &#39;Foundation&#39;s Edge&#39; to Asimov&#39;s short story &#39;The Last Question&#39;? If so, please let me know your thougts.</a>
