<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    I think Trevize was trying to communicate, not visualize. He could communicate with Terminus because it was near them. In order to communicate with fa<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    I think Trevize was trying to communicate, not visualize. He could communicate with Terminus because it was near them. In order to communicate with farther planets it would need a hyper relay. <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
