<div id="review_2020752584" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2020752584" />
    <a title="Adrian" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/22809267-adrian"><img alt="Adrian" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1484242635p2/22809267.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2020752584?book_show_action=true">Jul 03, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Adrian" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Adrian" href="/user/show/22809267-adrian">Adrian</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780586058398" href="/book/show/509829.Foundation_s_Edge">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/22809267-adrian?shelf=sci-fi">sci-fi</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/22809267-adrian?shelf=read-again">read-again</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/22809267-adrian?shelf=zz-owned-books">zz-owned-books</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/22809267-adrian?shelf=sf-robots-n-empire">sf-robots-n-empire</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2020752584" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7112207689633112156">Although written much later than the original Foundation trilogy, this book in my opinion is on a par with them. Not only is it a great story, well written as ever by Asimov, but after having read the Foundation novels, the Robot novels and the Empire novels (some many times), you realise how cleverly this book starts to bring everything together the way Asimov intended.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


